      "chain_name": "Weak JWT \u2192 SQL Injection \u2192 Prescription Tampering",
      "attack_scenario": "An attacker cracks or guesses the weak JWT secret, forging a Veterinarian ('VET') session token. They then use the SQL injection vulnerability on the pet search endpoint to enumerate pet IDs and find targeted records. Finally, they call the prescription update endpoint to alter controlled substance prescriptions undetected due to the absence of logging.",
